    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The engine starts up and runs consistently, and the transmission is functional, though shifts aren't as crisp as they once were. You will notice some cosmetic wear, including minor dents on the exterior and some staining and thinning of the upholstery inside. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who is prepared for some upcoming routine maintenance and minor repairs.",
